A teenage girl and her 27-year-old boyfriend are accused of murdering her 14-month-old brother on New Year's Day.

Tereza Lackova, 19, and her boyfriend Marek Holub, both of Balsall Heath, Birmingham, are jointly charged with murdering Lackova's baby brother Santino Balaz.

The unemployed pair are also charged with causing, or allowing, the death of a child.  

