Officers from West Midlands Police are now liaising with officials in the Czech Republic to trace Santino's mother.

She is believed to have returned to her home country in September last year.

Detective Inspector Justin Spanner said: We are awaiting further tests following a post-mortem.

'Santino was found to have extensive injuries and fractures to several areas of his body.'

